snippet.title: Battle Tanks: World War II (Promo Eng)
snippet.description:
Download now: https://battle-tanks.onelink.me/QBQc/yt8zb5vh
Exciting battles on tanks the Second World War! Fight for the honor of your country!
Promo code for newbies:
TOBATTLE

Meet the tank game - Battle Tanks
Fight in 10vs10 team battles alone or with friends, research and upgrade armored vehicles, try different tactics and win. 
Choose a tank and join the battle!

Play tanks online, fight on realistic maps, receive legendary vehicles, complete battle tasks and raise your reputation among all other players.

🔥 Play right now and join community! 🔥
📘 Facebook  -  https://www.facebook.com/battletanksgames
🎮 Discord - https://discord.gg/39g6CmXHyy
